{"tid":2289010,"cid":21,"subCid":4,"title":"無視小粉紅杯葛 推Be Water水樽  BTS撐黃傘陣 抗藍人圍堵","createTime":"2020-11-17T02:50:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T07:26:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0600c9c602410207bbf613260f1b092a77318fcc","tid":2289010,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T02:50:21.000Z","msg":"無視小粉紅杯葛 推Be Water水樽 <br />\nBTS撐黃傘陣 抗藍人圍堵<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201117/QA3JVVSPZVBELAUDHWFOMQG2CQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201117%2FQA3JVVSPZVBELAUDHWFOMQG2CQ%2F&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM43psBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=7489403a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201117%2FQA3JVVSPZVBELAUDHWFOMQG2CQ%2F&h=2d85e7d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201117/QA3JVVSPZVBELAUDHWFOMQG2CQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n韓國人氣男團防彈少年團（BTS）上月因提及韓戰而被內地小粉紅轟辱華，之後其所屬事務所又推出印有反送中時常用口號「be water」的樽裝水，舉動引發小粉紅在網上狂攻擊，不過已打開歐美市場的BTS冇有怕，近日事務所推出的新宣傳片中，除出現穿上黃色連帽外套的公仔被一群藍衣人包圍外，成員柾國又在另一宣傳片中穿黑衣兼拿着黃色雨傘現身，之後片中更出現黃色雨傘陣，網民認為連串舉動加起來，不是巧合那麼簡單！<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sojcXSt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsojcXSt.jpg&h=28667d18&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"056f33fe191948d2aa32aecdb21dcbcfb86c5ed6","tid":2289010,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T02:55:56.000Z","msg":"韓仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申唔識佢哋"},{"pid":"77d66f1e71ce3f6db7d4cb9f77a050dbab3a204a","tid":2289010,"uid":57303,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"056f33fe191948d2aa32aecdb21dcbcfb86c5ed6","tid":2289010,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T02:55:56.000Z","msg":"韓仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.