11-17T03:41:26.000Z","msg":"紅爆全球的韓國男團BTS，近日頻頻惹來內地網民攻擊，先有因提及韓戰而被轟辱華、再因推出印有「be water」的樽裝水而遭小粉紅鬧爆，但BTS未因要妥協內地市場賺人民幣而跪低致歉，BTS所屬的公司Big Hit前日公開有關《HIT IT 8 HIP HOP Competition》的比賽內容，又再觸及香港逆權運動！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/cRL2ONz86nmSv5ZMkGeFW4vySOo=/640x467/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TCSA47NS3VGD3HRED5L5RYL5EY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FcRL2ONz86nmSv5ZMkGeFW4vySOo%3D%2F640x467%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTCSA47NS3VGD3HRED5L5RYL5EY.jpg&h=e914662f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n傘下起舞 ■於預告片BTS成員手持黃傘背鏡跳舞，再演化出黃色雨傘陣，後來成員轉身擺甫士才知道是柾國。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1h8Ols0motd1HYXKFMeZzgx4ZGo=/640x467/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LAEOJ3353RC3LFBL2OZMFCZRDY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1h8Ols0motd1HYXKFMeZzgx4ZGo%3D%2F640x467%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLAEOJ3353RC3LFBL2OZMFCZRDY.jpg&h=cd0e4161&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n變出遮陣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3g3dUeV4QDV5UDWt7gEFd7Muwtg=/640x468/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/P7HI5PXCZ5C4XOYCDJIHUWJCAA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3g3dUeV4QDV5UDWt7gEFd7Muwtg%3D%2F640x468%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FP7HI5PXCZ5C4XOYCDJIHUWJCAA.jpg&h=48d5f67f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n柾國現身"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T04:07:28.000Z","msg":"「太多巧合加埋就唔係巧合」<br />\n<br />\n這個以十多歲rappers為對象的比賽，以「Ready for the Spotlight」作主題，但於海報及宣傳片中，竟湊巧以大堆藍色公仔為背景，中間站着的是穿上黃色連帽外套的角色，令人聯想到象徵香港抗爭者的黃色雨褸，畫面上更呈現「萬藍叢中一點黃」，別具含意。此外，BTS即將推出2021 SEASON&rsquo;S GREETINGS年曆組合，近日已陸續公開新相及預告片，於上周公開的預告片中，成員柾國穿着黑西裝拿着黃色雨傘現身，之後鏡頭出現多把黃色雨傘形成遮陣場面，像極香港抗爭運動中出現的遮陣，影片公開後立即引來香港網民關注及留言，「太多巧合加埋一齊就唔係巧合」、「明顯有意思」等，眼利網友還發現BTS微博於8月後只更新過一次，似要用行動證明無視內地網民炮轟及杯葛。<br />\n<br />\nBTS被疑是手足並非源自單一事件，Big Hit早前推出樽裝水，樽身上印有「be with you, beWATER with BTS」，由於在去年香港的反送中運動曾借用「Be Water」為口號，示威手法更席捲全球，沒理由Big Hit留意不到，而公司在宣傳時還指水樽圖案為BTS成員親手設計，有fans更將水樽與「Be Water」文宣並列，難免令人無限聯想。上月BTS因對促進韓美關係有貢獻獲得「James A. Van Fleet Award」，他們在發表得獎感言時提及韓戰，內地網民指這個獎是跟紀念韓戰中的美軍有關，認為有感謝美國的意思，批評BTS不尊重當年於戰爭中犧牲的中國人，涉嫌辱華，BTS內地fans就揚言放棄支持BTS。不過BTS早已放眼歐美，多得組合帶挈，Big Hit娛樂社長方時赫昨日公佈第三季度的業績，就算因武肺疫情影響，淨利潤仍有約1.9億港元，與去年同期對比，全年加上第一、二季，淨利潤更增長13%。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/p8JYsrvXAyeXSZAWaUbub24ladI=/640x336/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3W6SCIXL3ZDZHK2OSO4GCWW7BI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fp8JYsrvXAyeXSZAWaUbub24ladI%3D%2F640x336%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3W6SCIXL3ZDZHK2OSO4GCWW7BI.jpg&h=d083339c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■BTS推出樽身印上「Be Water」的樽裝水，有網友將水樽跟文宣並列，令人無限聯想。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/llgbofkM754oBpRqbWxWuoHfM3E=/640x297/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6XBKCH52EVE6LBBCU6I3WCH4VM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FllgbofkM754oBpRqbWxWuoHfM3E%3D%2F640x297%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6XBKCH52EVE6LBBCU6I3WCH4VM.jpg&h=9301e0db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■女團BLACK PINK的歌曲MV中有出現傘陣及燒傘場面，即遭網友懷疑暗示攬炒。"},{"pid":"236f5da0361c0ed38636e7f83de6d1892afa5e8c","tid":2289010,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"71a6020c53a7c692d375828c6f752a33fadddbe3","tid":2289010,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f01a3ad48abc37d916c