thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FV6iQ0U21EqTJlNJf6-Q7GlkG4Cs%3D%2F640x306%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPHZX454GDJCAVPZCIMJ4KZVXVQ.jpg&h=c8ee6954&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBLACK PINK焚傘寓意攬炒<br />\n<br />\n疑有韓國團體暗撐香港抗爭已不是首次，今年6月，同樣紅爆世界各地的韓國女團BLACK PINK推出新歌《How You Like That》，MV中由於出現眾多雨傘之後全遭焚毀，已被網友懷疑暗示攬炒，當中有成員戴起黑色蝙蝠面罩，則被指暗藏武漢肺炎等政治話題。適逢香港7.1遊行，成員Ros&eacute;於Ig即時動態上載一張於中環拍攝的黑白照，相片有一架由銅鑼灣出發的962號城巴經過，連登仔指Ros&eacute;叫人上街遊行，也有fans認為是美麗誤會。"},{"pid":"9984218750e4298ffaa82baf2f6a1ce7e035b756","tid":2289010,"uid":373254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T04:42:01.000Z","msg":"我係army<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4a17868e3a28fbe17e5eb510824113c6f3f708c","tid":2289010,"uid":113989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T05:09:09.000Z","msg":"Bp就太勉強了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10dbbed9d5ca7672f7dd60e0f6a8200b635f11fa","tid":2289010,"uid":257248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4a17868e3a28fbe17e5eb510824113c6f3f708c","tid":2289010,"uid":113989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T05:09:09.000Z","msg":"Bp就太勉強了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T05:24:55.000Z","msg":"仲會返微博買熱搜買營銷 <br />\n自動供錢比支"},{"pid":"e44fe40011e9111c29a759c8f8dac54e0e62947d","tid":2289010,"uid":113989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10dbbed9d5ca7672f7dd60e0f6a8200b635f11fa","tid":2289010,"uid":257248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4a17868e3a28fbe17e5eb510824113c6f3f708c","tid":2289010,"uid":113989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T05:09:09.000Z","msg":"Bp就太勉強了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T05:24:55.000Z","msg":"仲會返微博買熱搜買營銷 <br />\n自動供錢比支"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T07:26:46.000Z","msg":"Bts會參與創作，作品有個人意志係入面<br />\nBp呢種偶像團就算啦出嚟過下癮姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}